{"id":29637092863,"name":"Run api tests","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAG5oIl_w","head_branch":"perf/geofeatures-geom-prefilter-43_2.42","head_sha":"6c74a1ae79c17784a5ed2632eec5f84552815f9a","path":".github/workflows/run-api-tests.yml","run_number":51195,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"perf: pre-filter geoFeatures org units by geometry (#24279) [2.42]","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":5591308,"check_suite_id":80261795643,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAASr_nPOw","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29637092863","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29637092863","pull_requests":[{"id":4081664146,"number":24492,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/pulls/24492","head":{"ref":"perf/geofeatures-geom-prefilter-43_2.42","sha":"6c74a1ae79c17784a5ed2632eec5f84552815f9a","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}},"base":{"ref":"2.42","sha":"e8d9886826875da0569d71f98f6d87d2ad567ac3","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}}}],"created_at":"2026-07-18T08:13:28Z","updated_at":"2026-07-18T08:25:55Z","run_started_at":"2026-07-18T08:13:28Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29637092863/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29637092863/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/80261795643","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29637092863/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29637092863/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29637092863/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"perf: pre-filter geoFeatures org units by geometry (#24279)\n\n* perf: pre-filter geoFeatures org units by geometry\n\ngeoFeatures resolves the `ou` dimension into full OrganisationUnit\nentities, then discards every unit without geometry in-memory. On a\nlarge hierarchy (Nigeria prod: ~255k level-5 units, all null-geometry)\nthis hydrates a quarter-million entities — ~7.6s CPU and ~4.7 GB\nallocated — only to return [].\n\nThread an optional `geometryOnly` flag from DataQueryRequest through\nDimensionalObjectProvider and OrganisationUnitService down to\nHibernateOrganisationUnitStore, which appends `and o.geometry is not\nnull`. Default off, so all other callers dispatch the original 2-arg\nmethods unchanged. Skipped in geoJsonAttribute (coordinateField) mode,\nwhere coordinates come from an attribute and the geometry column may be\nnull. The in-memory filter remains the precise final gate.\n\nWhen the geometry-filtered resolution is empty, the E7143 empty-dimension\nguard is suppressed so geoFeatures still returns 200 [] rather than an\nerror.\n\nValidated on production (Nigeria, deployed on 2.40): a comparable\nhigh-level layer dropped from ~8.6s/4.7GB to 14ms/747KB.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\n\n* refactor: bundle getDimension args into DimensionResolveOptions\n\nThe private getDimension dispatcher grew to 8 parameters when geometryOnly\nwas threaded through, tripping SonarQube java:S107 (\u003e7 parameters). Bundle\nthe five resolution options (relativePeriodDate, displayProperty, allowNull,\ninputIdScheme, geometryOnly) into a private DimensionResolveOptions record,\nbringing the method to 4 parameters. Behaviour is unchanged; contained\nentirely within DefaultDataQueryService.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"},"id":"6c74a1ae79c17784a5ed2632eec5f84552815f9a","tree_id":"9662262478dbce4ce284d28577b842b392b6f059","timestamp":"2026-07-18T08:07:29Z","c